Burrhus Frederic Skinner kɛ ɛyʊ weyi ɛlaba ɛyʊ fitenum sukuli yɔ ɛkɛ mazɩyʊ Amerika ɛjaɖɛ taa. Ivan Pavlove tʊma kaañaɣ ɛ-yɔɔ piŋ ɛ nɛ John Watson. Palʊla Sinner pɩnaɣ 1904 [[Pɛnsilvaanii|Pennsylvani]] kɛ [[Etaazuunii]] ɛjaɖɛ taa.
[[Fichier:Skinner_teaching_machine_07.jpg|vignette|Skinner teaching machine 07]]
Ɛmʊ sukuli sɔsɔʊ taa takayaɣ ŋga kawɩlɩɣ se ɛkɛ sukuli pɩɣa sɔsɔ yɔ lɛ kɛ ''Hamilton College'' taa [[Aŋgɩlɩtɛɛrɩ|Ɛŋglɩsɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ pɩnaɣ 1926 lɛ ɛkpaɣ lɩmaɣza mbʊ se ɛtɛzʊʊ ɛ-tɛ kpɛlɛkɩtʊ sukuli kɛ [[Harvard sukulɩ kɩtɛzʊʊ|Harvard sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ]] taa, peeɖe ɛmʊ ɛyʊ fetenum kpɛlɛkʊʊ takayaɣ sɔsɔ pɩnaɣ 1931. Peeɖe ɛcaɣ pɩkɔɔ pɩsɩna pɩnaɣ ŋga 1936 ɛ-tɛ kpɛlɛkɩtʊ nɔmɔʊ taa. Ɛwɩlɩ sukuli [[Minesootaa|Minnesota]] sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ taa, ɛpɩsɩ peeɖe sukuli ŋgʊ kɩ-taa takʊʊ nɛ wiluu tʊmɩyɛ ñʊʊ tʊ kɛ Indiana sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ taa pɩnaɣ 1945. 

Ɛpɩsɩ sukuli kɩtɛzʊʊ ŋgʊ kɩ-taa pɩnaɣ 1948, nɛ pɛkpɛlɛkɩ-ɩ ɛyʊ fitenum tɔm camɩyɛ nɛ ɛwɛɛ tʊmɩyɛ ndɩ ɖɩ-yɔɔ halɩ ɛkɔɔ ewolo hɛzʊʊ pɩnaɣ 1974. Ɛsɩpɩna calɩm pɩcɛɖɛ kʊdɔŋ [[Kɩyɛɛna fenaɣ|kɩyɛna fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 18 pɩnaɣ 1990. Pepimi-ɩ Mount Auburn pɩlaŋ yɔɔ. Burrhus Frederic Skinner kɛ ɛyʊ weyi ɛlaba ɛyʊ fitenum sukuli yɔ ɛkɛ mazɩyʊ Amerika ɛjaɖɛ taa. Ivan Pavlove tʊma kaañaɣ ɛ-yɔɔ piŋ ɛ nɛ John Watson.
